author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
Did any MythBusters conclusion result in the scientific community reevaluating its findings? In this live stream excerpt, Adam Savage answers this question from Tested member J_Dellarosa, whom we thank for their support! 

Where Was the Real Science in MythBusters? https://youtu.be/_MUtHQLb_MA
The Myth the MythBusters Refused to Touch: https://youtu.be/nYHi8PLjczw
How Lead Balloon Changed MythBusters: https://youtu.be/h70kbIzPgig
The MythBusters Episode Adam Savage Regrets Making: https://youtu.be/0y2fDrv47U4
